            │  M          Toggle metrics panel (compact/expanded)  │            
            │  L          Change target language                   │            
            │  S          Settings (F2/Ctrl+D cycles field values) │            
            │  R          Reload config from disk                  │            
            │  ?          Show / hide this help                    │            
            │  Esc        Dismiss this overlay                     │            
            │  Tab        Switch A/B pane focus (dual-slot mode)   │            
            │  q / Ctrl+C Quit — shows session summary             │            
